  Upstream Fidelity (25%):  {score}/10  {one-line justification}
  Completeness      (20%):  {score}/10  {one-line justification}
  Business Meaning  (15%):  {score}/10  {one-line justification}
  Shape Fidelity    (10%):  {score}/10  {one-line justification}

WEIGHTED SCORE: {N.N}/10

VERDICT: {PASS / FAIL}

SPECIFIC ISSUES (if FAIL):
  1. {Column X}: Assigned Tier 2 but upstream wiki Trade.PositionTbl has matching column with description "..." — should be Tier 1
  2. {Column Y}: Description says "..." but upstream wiki says "..." — not verbatim
  3. Section 1: Missing row count and date range — too vague
  ...

REGENERATION FEEDBACK (if FAIL):
  Re-run Phase 11 with these corrections:
  - Read Trade.PositionTbl upstream wiki column {X} and copy description verbatim as Tier 1
  - Add row count from Phase 2 to Section 1 summary
  - ...
```

